==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Turner
<hw>Tur"ner</hw> <pr>(t⟦oomac⟧r"n⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[G.]</ety> <def>A person who practices athletic or gymnastic
